{"tid":2369660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"aespa出道61天拿一位！少時後新紀錄　腦粉CUE「師兄沒拿過」戰爆","createTime":"2021-01-17T10:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T19:39:38.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1534206318a16f52581b85849c8c6bf14d911388","tid":2369660,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"南韓最大造星工廠SM娛樂推出的新女團aespa，還沒出道就有高討論度，儘管一度受到負面評論攻擊，但出道後依舊證明了自己的實力和魅力，在17日拿下音樂節目「初一位」。也是繼少女時代出道14年來，SM娛樂女團的新紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5402/d5402260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5402%2Fd5402260.jpg&h=2507d3a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲aespa出道61天拿一位。（圖／翻攝自官方推特）<br />\naespa儘管打歌期已經結束，17日在SBS的《人氣歌謠》拿下初一位，甚至打敗了近來翻紅的Rain與JYP朴軫永的合作曲《Switch to me》。這是也是SM娛樂繼「少女時代」出道14年後，首次有女團以出道曲拿下一位，過去f(x)和Red Velvet都沒有拿到這項指標。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5402/d5402261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5402%2Fd5402261.jpg&h=e9add33d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲aespa打敗Rain與朴軫永的合作曲，出道61天拿到「初一位」。（圖／翻攝自SBS）<br />\n<br />\naespa成員Winter是元旦寶寶，在今年1月1日生日時，她的願望之一就是「希望今年能拿到一位」，沒想到17天後就成真，也讓粉絲為她們開心和激動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5402/d5402250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5402%2Fd5402250.jpg&h=1c8aef66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲部分aespa粉絲酸NCT沒拿過一位。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n不過該團部分大陸粉絲興奮之餘卻說出：「有一個師兄團出道至今還沒拿過一位，我不說是誰。」暗酸NCT，同時也有部分粉絲響應：「太好笑了。」、「好缺德但好好笑」，讓NCT粉絲反彈：「是飯隨愛豆愛嘴人？」指成員Karina出道前曾疑似被爆出酸公司和前輩的對話紀錄，雙方粉絲再度開戰。不過大部分aespa也反感這樣的行為，痛罵這些人：「無腦，不要給偶像招黑！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5292/d5292622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5292%2Fd5292622.jpg&h=6bb6d31a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲NCT共有23人分成小分隊活動，去年度專輯總銷量破500萬。（圖／avex taiwan提供）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZxOxWJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZxOxWJ.png&h=dd9f7301&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bc6d1ab263d334d16a1e660800a59dc97a90d93","tid":2369660,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:42:07.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5579d80aaba0fc74e73ef55092e3bb3a8811e5ea","tid":2369660,"uid":177639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe71d8bdb2660936653fd485ea98cf34157f32d","tid":2369660,"uid":134171,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"nct 真係好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8ca54a412684df50dedb0a62168904c8788594","tid":2369660,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"冇興趣睇個兩件大叔啦"},{"pid":"f3584aa9be4e6405868303c349c38a10d064d3d8","tid":2369660,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"NCT<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a2d1282083a13b91c4c95d983570107ec12809","tid":2369660,"uid":68678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae8ca54a412684df50dedb0a62168904c8788594","tid":2369660,"uid":190258,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:49